### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Create article
### POST /articles
### Requires: JWT auth cookie
### Body: multipart/form-data
###   - title: string
###   - description: string
###   - sections: JSON array [{ title, content }]
###   - hashtags: JSON array (optional)
###   - coverImage: file (optional, max 5MB)
### Returns: Created article
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST http://localhost:8080/articles
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary123

--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

My Article Title
--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

This is a brief description of the article
--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="sections"

[{"title": "Introduction", "content": "This is the intro..."}, {"title": "Main Part", "content": "This is the main content..."}]
--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="hashtags"

["Technology", "Programming", "NestJS"]
--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="coverImage"; filename="cover.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./cover.jpg
--boundary123--

